front.title: H.248 Annex F (Fax, Text Conversation, and Call discrimination))

abstract.t: This document reproduces the content of the ITU-T Study Group 16 White Document draft of H.248 Annex F, which was decided in Geneva in November 2000. It also includes minor corrections made in January 2001. This document is submitted for IETF in accordance with procedures currently being negotiated between ITU-T Study Group and ISOC on behalf of the IETF.
